high_descs: Walk over to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Put the tomato in fridge for a couple seconds to get cold, then take it out.
Walk over to the microwave above the stove.
Put the chilled tomato in a microwave that left the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk over to the cabinet with a spoon and a salt shaker.
Put the tomato in the cabinet and take it out while opening and closing it.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, move past the fridge, then face the counter on your right.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Bring the tomato to the fridge on the right.
Chill the tomato in the fridge for a few seconds.
Bring the chilled tomato back to the microwave over the stove on the right.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.
